'''Alabama Luella Barker''' (born December 24, 2005) is an [[Americans|American]] media personality. She is the daughter of [[Blink-182]] drummer [[Travis Barker]] and his ex-wife, actress [[Shanna Moakler]].<ref name=":0">{{Cite web |title=Travis Barker and Shanna Moakler's Relationship: A Look Back |url=https://people.com/travis-barker-shanna-moakler-timeline-7502334#:~:text=Barker%20and%20Moakler%20welcomed%20daughter%20Alabama%20Luella%20on,I'm%20hoping%20for%20a%20girl,%22%20the%20drummer%20said. |access-date=2025-01-05 |website=People.com |language=en}}</ref><ref name=":1">{{Cite web |last=Wabwile |first=Alice |date=2024-11-24 |title=Alabama Barker's age and bio: Key facts about Travis Barker's daughter |url=https://briefly.co.za/facts-lifehacks/celebrities-biographies/203075-alabama-barkers-age-bio-key-facts-travis-barkers-daughter/ |access-date=2025-01-05 |website=Briefly |language=en}}</ref> In 2022, her father married [[Kourtney Kardashian]], making Alabama her [[Stepchild|step-daughter]].<ref>{{Cite web |title=Kourtney Kardashian and Travis Barker's Relationship Timeline |url=https://people.com/tv/kourtney-kardashian-and-travis-barker-relationship-timeline/ |access-date=2025-01-05 |website=People.com |language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |date=2024-12-30 |title=Kourtney Kardashian Shares Holiday Pics With Travis Barker and Baby Rocky |url=https://www.elle.com/culture/celebrities/a44666889/travis-barker-kourtney-kardashian-relationship-timeline/ |access-date=2025-01-05 |website=ELLE |language=en-US}}</ref><ref name=":2">{{Cite web |title=Kourtney Kardashian and Travis Barker Get Legally Married |url=https://www.etonline.com/kourtney-kardashian-and-travis-barker-get-legally-married-in-santa-barbara-182192 |access-date=2025-01-05 |website=Entertainment Tonight |language=en-US}}</ref>

